creator: Alaan
descriptionHtml:
Alaan is Middle East's first multi-currency spend management platform to manage all company spend through corporate cards and automated invoice payments.

With Alaan mobile app, you can:

✅ Get real-time notifications when you spend using your Alaan corporate card.

✅ Track your business expenses in real-time.

✅ See your card details, freeze and unfreeze your cards.

✅ Get rid of expense reports completely.

✅ Take a photo of your receipt, categorize the expense and add a memo immediately.

About Alaan:

Our mission is to simplify finance for underserved businesses in the Middle East and help them prosper. With Alaan, businesses can issue unlimited corporate cards in multiple currencies, including AED, SAR, USD and more. Additionally, finance teams can automatically schedule Invoice payments with no manual effort and simplify bookkeeping by integrating with their preferred accounting software.

We are obsessed with helping underserved SMEs and entrepreneurs spend smarter and easier.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Added Pull-To-Refresh, Card Delivery Edit address option & Card Velocity Info Features & UI enhancement

descriptionHtml:
